data.description: This Beautiful Move-In Ready home features 2381 sq. ft of comfortable living space in a sought-after neighborhood.  Fantastic open floor plan, high ceilings, 4 bedrooms, 3 baths plus Office/den & oversized 3 car garage. This the perfect place to call home! Large open Chef's kitchen with center island, granite countertops, high-end stainless steel appliances, large pantry, breakfast nook and ample cabinet space. Perfect place to prepare delicious meals and entertain guest. Open Concept Living/Dining Room, Large Master Suite with spacious walk-in closet. Beautiful Master bath with dual sinks. Large Fenced Yard on .34 acre lot, Plenty of Room for a pool and RV. Fruit Trees, Roof 2019, A/C 2019.  Location is key! Close to all, great shopping & dining, restaurants, Cape Coral bridge. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home. Schedule your showing today to immerse yourself in everything this property has to offer!
